paragraphs.text:
%hive
SELECT t2.vehicle_id,
    t2.trip_id,
    t2.ft_count_vehicle_deaccel_val,
    t4.ft_count_vehicle_accel_val,
    t6.ft_sum_hard_brakes_10_flg_val
FROM (
    SELECT vehicle_id, trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_count_vehicle_deaccel_val
    FROM (
        SELECT vehicle_id, trip_id, acceleration_group
        FROM drive_temp
        -- WHERE vehicle_id = 1000500 AND trip_id = "152af94305154e5681323461de8e4ce6"
        GROUP BY vehicle_id, trip_id, acceleration_group
        HAVING MIN(acceleration) < 0
    ) t1
    GROUP BY vehicle_id, trip_id
) t2
JOIN
(
    SELECT vehicle_id, trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_count_vehicle_accel_val
    FROM (
        SELECT vehicle_id, trip_id, acceleration_group
        FROM drive_temp
        -- WHERE vehicle_id = 1000500 AND trip_id = "152af94305154e5681323461de8e4ce6"
        GROUP BY vehicle_id, trip_id, acceleration_group
        HAVING MAX(acceleration) > 0
    ) t3
    GROUP BY vehicle_id, trip_id
) t4
ON t2.vehicle_id = t4.vehicle_id AND t2.trip_id = t4.trip_id
JOIN
(
    SELECT vehicle_id, trip_id, COUNT(*) AS ft_sum_hard_brakes_10_flg_val
    FROM (
        SELECT vehicle_id, trip_id, acceleration_group
        FROM drive_temp
        -- WHERE vehicle_id = 1000500 AND trip_id = "152af94305154e5681323461de8e4ce6"
        GROUP BY vehicle_id, trip_id, acceleration_group
        HAVING MIN(acceleration) <= -10
    ) t5
    GROUP BY vehicle_id, trip_id
) t6
ON t2.vehicle_id = t6.vehicle_id AND t2.trip_id = t6.trip_id
